He did gives us God's plan for marriage - see Matthew 19. He makes it very clear that marriage -as designed by the Creator and the Sovereign of the Universe - that marriage is a lifelong, monogamous, sexual union between one man and one woman.Jesus said nothing about a lot of things. The absence of specific statements about specific things cannot reasonably be extrpolated to infer He had no opinion, as can be seen by the example just given.